          "scid": "an4.229:1.1",
          "pli": "… pe … Assaddho hoti, dussīlo hoti, ahiriko hoti, anottappī hoti … pe … saddho hoti, sīlavā hoti, hirimā hoti, ottappī hoti … pe …. ",
          "en": "“A foolish person … makes much bad karma. … They’re faithless, unethical, shameless, and imprudent. … An astute person … makes much merit. … They’re faithful, ethical, conscientious, and prudent. …” "
